Introduction Researchers in both machine lranslation (e.g. , Brown et al, 1990) and bilingual lexicography (e.g. , Klavans and Tzoukermann, 1990) have recently become interested in studying bilingual corpora, bodies of text such as the Canadian I-lansards (parliamentary debates) which are available in multiple languages (such as French and English). 
